snippet.title: Skull Island: Rise of Kong Available Now
snippet.description: Take on an action-packed quest to avenge the death of Kong’s parents at the hands of the ultimate alpha predator: the saurian terror Gaw. Traverse the mysterious island and uncover its secrets across a variety of treacherous environments, discovering the power coursing through its exotic flora and fauna. Conquer waves of primal beasts, defeat unique bosses, and rise above all who stand in Kong’s way to being King! Play on Nintendo Switch, Playstation 4|5, Steam and Xbox today!
